Warning

This function was DEPRECATED in PHP 4.1.0, and REMOVED in PHP 7.0.0.

Alternatives to this function include:

 * |call_user_func|

===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  call_user_method ( string $method_name , object &$obj [, mixed $... ] ) :~
  mixed~

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{method_name}

  The method name being called.

{obj}

  The object that {method_name} is being called on.

{...}

  The optional parameters.

===============================================================================
[ Examples ]

Example #1 call_user_method() alternative

<?php >
  call_user_func(array($obj, $method_name), $parameter /* , ... */);
<?>

===============================================================================
[ See Also ]

 * |call_user_func_array| - Call a callback with an array of parameters
 * |call_user_func| - Call the callback given by the first parameter


